### ============================================
### Settings API — /api/settings
### See AUTH.md for how to get a session cookie.
### ============================================

@base = http://localhost:5050
@cookie = better-auth.session_token=PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE


### ─── GET settings (creates default if none exist) ───

GET {{base}}/api/settings
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### ─── PUT settings (partial update — merges, doesn't replace) ───

PUT {{base}}/api/settings
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": "light",
  "defaultView": "list"
}

### ─── PUT settings — toggle booleans ───

PUT {{base}}/api/settings
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "autoFetch": false,
  "aiSummary": false,
  "weeklyDigest": true
}

### ─── Verify merge — GET should show all keys ───

GET {{base}}/api/settings
Cookie: {{cookie}}


### ============================================
### VALIDATION TESTS — expect 400 errors
### ============================================

### ─── Object value (injection attempt) ───

PUT {{base}}/api/settings
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": {"$gt": ""}
}

### ─── Array value ───

PUT {{base}}/api/settings
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": [1, 2, 3]
}

### ─── String too long (> 200 chars) ───

PUT {{base}}/api/settings
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA"
}

### ─── Unknown keys stripped ───

PUT {{base}}/api/settings
Cookie: {{cookie}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": "dark",
  "evil": "should-be-stripped",
  "__proto__": {"admin": true}
}

### ─── No auth (expect 401) ───

GET {{base}}/api/settings
